      Cuisinart Advantage 12pc Color Knife Set with Blade Guards


      PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS

      • High-quality stainless steel blades
      • Non-stick color coating for easy slicing
      • Color coding reduces the risk of cross-contamination during food preparation
      • Comes with matching blade guards and ergonomic handles
      • Style-conscious hues


      These Stainless steel knives are tailored for both heavy duty chopping as well as intricate knife work. Each knife is accompanied by a color-coded blade guard that not only protects nearby fingers but also staves off premature blade dulling.


      Cuisinart Advantage 12-Piece Set Contents

      • 8? chef’s knife with guard
      • 8? slicing knife with guard
      • 8? bread knife with guard
      • 7? santoku knife with guard
      • 5.5? utility knife with guard
      • 3.5? paring knife with guard

      Data Recovery

      Why would I need DriveSavers Data Recovery Service Plan?
      • Devices fail. Mother Nature strikes. People make mistakes.
      • A device warranty covers repairs and replacements only.
      • Your data will be lost forever.
      Can't I just run recovery software?
      • 85% of all data loss is due to physical or electro-mechanical failure.
      • Data recovery software is not a solution in this scenario.
      • Running it could wipe your data off the drive.
      What else do I need to know?
      • DriveSavers Data Recovery Advisors are available 24 hours a day to assist you.
      • Our service plan redemption is quick and hassle-free.
      • DriveSavers engineers are the best in the business!
      How do I request Service?
      • Request service online at https://newegg.drivesavers.com
      • Contact a live person 24/7 at (800)-440-1904
      • Click here for the Terms & Conditions of this Plan.
